text: Hypercourt is a commune. It is in Hauts-de-France in the Somme department in north France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Pertain (the seat), Hyencourt-le-Grand and Omiécourt.Arrêté préfectoral 25 May 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Somme
title: Hypercourt
